 Children of Men: Don’t Ignore the Background 

 
 posted by  Jason Kottke     Sep 15, 2015 
 

 

 



 The Nerdwriter takes on Children of Men, specifically what’s going in the background of Alfonso Cuarón’s film, both in terms of references to other works of art &amp; culture and to things that push the plot along and contribute to the tone and message of the film. 


